NVIDIA ONGOING ISSUE 2: - SOLVED: HOW TO START NVIDIA FAN
nvidia fan not working on latest Drivers:
Xorg needs to be running as root!

Check that you're not running Xorg as an user:
	ps -o user $(pgrep Xorg)

