SHORTCUT/HOTKEYS
COMMON TEXT EDITOR SHORTCUT KEYS:
ctrl+a				#Start of Line 
ctrl+e 				#End of Line

TERMINOLOGY/YAKUAKE/SOME TERMINALS SHORTCUT/HOTKEYS KEYS:
