ENABLING VSYNC FOR NVIDIA

1. Install nvidia-utils and all drivers, then type: $nvidia-settings
2. Go to 'X Server Display Configuration'
3. Go to 'Advanced Settings'
4. Check 'Force Full Compositition Pipeline'
5. Click Apply

