--------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------
NON-STOCK / CUSTOM KERNELS
	linux-zen, linux-pds, linux-tkg-pds, liquorix(linux-zen for debian users), linux-xanmod.

Avoid linux-tkg actually, it has dropped fsync support and considered it Deprecated.
